WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 21=

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:42.840
Son!

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:43.680
Mom?

00:01:43.740 --> 00:01:44.590
Dad?

00:01:44.590 --> 00:01:45.760
What are you doing here?

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:46.920
I...

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:49.280
You're early. What day is it today?

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.200
Give that to me.

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:51.430
Your dad... He...

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.070
He can't stand being cooped up at home.

00:01:54.350 --> 00:01:56.230
And I'm bored out of my mind.

00:01:56.230 --> 00:01:57.430
So we came early.

00:01:57.430 --> 00:01:58.950
We'll head back after the check-up.

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:01.000
Why didn't you let me down?

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:02.920
I've been swamped with drafts lately.

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:04.040
It's fine.

00:02:05.070 --> 00:02:06.560
We've been here before.

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:08.240
We can take care of ourselves.

00:02:09.590 --> 00:02:10.430
Well...

00:02:10.540 --> 00:02:11.400
Do we need to

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:12.840
reschedule the check-up?

00:02:13.190 --> 00:02:14.630
It's all done.

00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:16.910
We're not some old fools.

00:02:16.910 --> 00:02:18.590
After you showed me last time,

00:02:19.150 --> 00:02:20.400
I've got the hang of it.

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:21.310
Pretty smart, huh?

00:02:21.310 --> 00:02:22.150
Okay, okay.

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:23.750
You guys are sharper than me.

00:02:25.150 --> 00:02:25.990
What?

00:02:26.240 --> 00:02:27.080
What did you say?

00:02:27.630 --> 00:02:28.560
Smart.

00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:29.710
He said you're smart.

00:02:31.190 --> 00:02:32.030
Son,

00:02:32.710 --> 00:02:35.030
why don't you ask Yu He out tonight?

00:02:35.630 --> 00:02:37.630
Let's have dinner together.

00:02:38.910 --> 00:02:40.910
I just praised you for being sharp.

00:02:42.310 --> 00:02:44.430
It's been ages. We broke up long ago.

00:02:46.080 --> 00:02:47.270
- Broke up?
- What did he say?

00:02:49.190 --> 00:02:50.030
Broke up.

00:02:50.710 --> 00:02:51.550
What?

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:54.750
He broke up with Yu He.

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:56.640
They split up.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:02:59.840
Son,

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:01.800
when did this happen?

00:03:02.630 --> 00:03:04.080
I told you before.

00:03:04.630 --> 00:03:06.400
When did you tell me?

00:03:06.680 --> 00:03:07.630
See?

00:03:07.630 --> 00:03:08.960
You're exploiting my bad hearing.

00:03:09.190 --> 00:03:11.430
Was it because of that fight last time?

00:03:11.430 --> 00:03:12.270
I even called her

00:03:12.270 --> 00:03:13.560
about it.

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:14.710
She said it was fine.

00:03:14.710 --> 00:03:16.150
So why did you break up?

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:19.680
Wait.

00:03:20.240 --> 00:03:21.080
Let me ask you.

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:23.560
Why did you break up with her?

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:25.000
It's over. That's all.

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:26.280
Just drop it.

00:03:26.710 --> 00:03:28.870
What makes you think you can do that?

00:03:28.870 --> 00:03:30.080
Look at that girl.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:31.750
She's a decent person,

00:03:32.030 --> 00:03:33.630
working as a clerk at a public office.

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:35.150
That's a stable job.

00:03:35.960 --> 00:03:37.590
She's well-educated.

00:03:38.030 --> 00:03:39.630
She has a good job.

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:42.190
And she's quite pretty.

00:03:43.310 --> 00:03:45.080
Look at you, bumming around all day,

00:03:45.080 --> 00:03:46.560
idling your life away.

00:03:46.750 --> 00:03:48.560
Can't you get a proper job?

00:03:49.710 --> 00:03:52.280
If you could marry that girl,

00:03:52.430 --> 00:03:54.590
you'd be punching way above your weight.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:58.240
How am I bumming around

00:03:58.240 --> 00:03:59.400
all day to you?

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:02.310
I draw comics every day.

00:04:02.310 --> 00:04:03.910
That is my job.

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:07.310
What kind of job is that?

00:04:09.310 --> 00:04:10.870
I've got to say this even if you hate it.

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:12.280
Your mom and I don't

00:04:12.430 --> 00:04:14.240
even know how to explain to relatives

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.360
what you do for a living.

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:17.750
You just draw all this

00:04:18.310 --> 00:04:19.870
messy stuff all day.

00:04:19.870 --> 00:04:20.920
That's comics?

00:04:20.920 --> 00:04:22.190
Comics are your job?

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:23.870
What's wrong with you?

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:27.070
You finally had a proper relationship.

00:04:27.070 --> 00:04:29.720
You should seize the chance and settle down.

00:04:29.920 --> 00:04:30.950
That way, your mom and I

00:04:31.120 --> 00:04:32.920
can finally stop stressing over you.

00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:34.830
I've got a feeling that if I get married,

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:37.600
you'll only find more things to worry about.

00:04:38.190 --> 00:04:39.510
Why does one have to get married?

00:04:39.510 --> 00:04:40.360
What did you say?

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:41.520
Speak louder.

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:43.870
Why don't you want get married?

00:04:43.870 --> 00:04:44.830
Why do I have to?

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:46.000
To fight all the time?

00:04:46.270 --> 00:04:47.680
You have been married for years.

00:04:47.830 --> 00:04:49.120
And you've always been fighting.

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:50.000
Is that fun?

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.310
Watch your tone!

00:04:52.870 --> 00:04:54.310
I think marriage has no meaning.

00:04:56.310 --> 00:04:57.560
Listen to your son.

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.000
If you don't get married,

00:04:59.190 --> 00:05:00.310
you'll just fool around alone.

00:05:00.630 --> 00:05:03.240
Look at this pigsty.

00:05:03.240 --> 00:05:05.190
Is this any way for a person to live?

00:05:08.750 --> 00:05:09.720
- Alright.
- That's enough.

00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:10.720
Calm down, calm down.

00:05:11.190 --> 00:05:13.160
I think I'm doing great right now.

00:05:13.430 --> 00:05:15.310
I eat, drink, and enjoy myself whenever I want.

00:05:15.510 --> 00:05:16.390
When I feel like working,

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:17.680
I draw some comics.

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:19.040
When I'm tired, I go have some fun.

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:20.320
I'm pretty free.

00:05:20.630 --> 00:05:21.830
What are you saying?

00:05:22.920 --> 00:05:24.750
We want you to settle down for your own sake.

00:05:24.750 --> 00:05:25.600
Do you understand?

00:05:26.600 --> 00:05:27.440
Hold on.

00:05:27.750 --> 00:05:28.870
Take that thing off.

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:31.920
I'm warning you.

00:05:32.480 --> 00:05:35.560
If you don't seriously get a girlfriend,

00:05:35.920 --> 00:05:37.560
don't come home for the New Year.

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:39.160
We can't handle that shame.

00:05:39.160 --> 00:05:40.680
Fine, I won't go home.

00:05:41.480 --> 00:05:42.430
It'll be quieter that way.

00:05:42.430 --> 00:05:43.270
Fine.

00:05:44.480 --> 00:05:46.160
Why pick a fight with your dad?

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:47.750
Your dad... He...

00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:51.190
Can't you just let him have it?

00:05:51.190 --> 00:05:52.950
Stop being so childish.

00:05:53.510 --> 00:05:54.560
He started it.

00:05:55.070 --> 00:05:56.270
I'm not as patient as you.

00:05:56.680 --> 00:05:57.520
Let's go.

00:05:59.220 --> 00:06:00.070
I...

00:06:00.070 --> 00:06:01.240
The old one and the young one

00:06:01.240 --> 00:06:02.720
can really wear me out.

00:06:14.830 --> 00:06:15.750
Was that woman

00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:17.040
really Sen's girlfriend?

00:06:17.430 --> 00:06:18.270
Yeah.

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:20.560
Sen even recommended me that shop

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:21.480
for our wedding photos.

00:06:21.950 --> 00:06:23.430
He said the owner was his girlfriend.

00:06:24.310 --> 00:06:25.600
Good thing I didn't go.

00:06:25.830 --> 00:06:27.270
A homewrecker shooting wedding photos?

00:06:27.430 --> 00:06:28.270
That's a total jinx.

00:06:29.160 --> 00:06:30.000
Still,

00:06:30.190 --> 00:06:32.240
no wonder Sen was so quiet this morning.

00:06:32.750 --> 00:06:33.750
I feel sorry for him.

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:35.830
Anyone would feel humiliated.

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:37.870
Do you think Sen will break up with her?

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:39.240
Who knows how long

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:40.720
she's been the other woman.

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:42.120
I'm afraid Sen's

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:43.310
been cheated all along.

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:44.950
He'll definitely break up with her.

00:06:45.310 --> 00:06:46.150
Let's go.

00:06:46.630 --> 00:06:48.240
Seriously, who could put up with that?

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:51.510
But if it was just for fun, no harm done.

00:06:52.190 --> 00:06:53.030
Keep it down.

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:54.830
Hello. Welcome.

00:06:57.310 --> 00:06:58.150
No need for that.

00:06:58.720 --> 00:06:59.600
I want a refund.

00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:01.240
May I ask why?

00:07:01.240 --> 00:07:02.830
We can't process refunds without a reason.

00:07:02.830 --> 00:07:04.800
No reason. I just don't want the shoot.

00:07:04.950 --> 00:07:06.040
Miss, you placed the order...

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:06.880
Wan.

00:07:08.040 --> 00:07:09.560
Are you sure you want to cancel

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:10.430
and get a refund?

00:07:12.070 --> 00:07:12.920
Yyu,

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:14.510
check if the makeup looks are set.

00:07:16.200 --> 00:07:17.040
No,

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:18.750
they just booked and paid the deposit.

00:07:19.270 --> 00:07:20.110
Alright.

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:22.000
Give them a full refund.

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:23.400
Yes.

00:07:23.750 --> 00:07:24.750
We'll process it now.

00:07:24.750 --> 00:07:25.870
It should reach you soon.

00:07:26.950 --> 00:07:28.480
Stop staring! Never seen a woman?

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:29.840
I'm not.

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:31.750
Shame on you.

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:34.310
Hey, don't be mad.

00:07:34.310 --> 00:07:35.870
- Wan, see them out.
- Alright, alright.

00:07:38.830 --> 00:07:40.630
Yyu, go confirm the rest

00:07:40.630 --> 00:07:41.750
of the appointments.

00:07:48.430 --> 00:07:50.000
How come you're off work so early today?

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.800
(Qian Chang Photography Studio)

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:53.120
I've got a clear afternoon.

00:07:53.430 --> 00:07:54.360
So I left early.

00:07:56.240 --> 00:07:57.560
It's fine. Don't worry about me.

00:08:01.950 --> 00:08:02.800
Maybe we should

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:04.000
close the shop for a while.

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:05.820
- After this...
- No way.

00:08:06.630 --> 00:08:08.070
If we close now, we might never reopen.

00:08:08.430 --> 00:08:10.360
Besides, we still owe Bei money.

00:08:10.680 --> 00:08:11.950
I'll figure something out.

00:08:17.510 --> 00:08:18.560
I don't want you hearing

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:19.870
those nasty rumors anymore.

00:08:23.070 --> 00:08:23.910
It's okay.

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:25.240
I can handle it.

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:30.440
Or do you think

00:08:32.510 --> 00:08:33.920
I'm an embarrassment to you?

00:08:33.980 --> 00:08:34.720
No.

00:08:35.390 --> 00:08:36.600
That's not it at all.

00:08:38.550 --> 00:08:39.790
Just forget what I said.

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:43.480
But if anyone causes trouble again,

00:08:44.150 --> 00:08:45.360
tell me immediately.

00:08:47.510 --> 00:08:48.350
I will.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.440
I need to go back to work.

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:52.480
You should leave. Okay?

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:53.840
See you at home tonight.

00:09:00.270 --> 00:09:01.270
Do you still trust him?

00:09:03.670 --> 00:09:05.240
Rationally speaking,

00:09:05.720 --> 00:09:07.240
if they got back together,

00:09:07.510 --> 00:09:09.480
his ex wouldn't show up and make a scene,

00:09:09.480 --> 00:09:10.320
would she?

00:09:10.600 --> 00:09:12.120
I want to know how you feel emotionally.

00:09:12.510 --> 00:09:14.270
Emotionally speaking,

00:09:15.870 --> 00:09:17.480
I can't stop doubting him.

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:19.600
Why don't you trust me?

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:21.960
What do I have to do to make you believe me?

00:09:22.390 --> 00:09:23.390
It's my own issue.

00:09:25.750 --> 00:09:27.360
I think I'm being ridiculous.

00:09:28.870 --> 00:09:30.030
You didn't text me back

00:09:30.030 --> 00:09:31.390
while I was watching the play.

00:09:31.670 --> 00:09:32.670
My mind ran wild:

00:09:33.480 --> 00:09:35.550
"What are you doing? Who are you with?"

00:09:36.630 --> 00:09:37.750
When I came over just now,

00:09:37.750 --> 00:09:39.270
I was ready to catch you cheating.

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:43.270
I felt like I was acting like

00:09:43.870 --> 00:09:45.200
a self-righteous clown.

00:09:45.550 --> 00:09:46.840
You should be like this.

00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:49.630
You care because you like me.

00:09:50.150 --> 00:09:51.390
And because I like you,

00:09:51.390 --> 00:09:53.240
I don't think you're a clown at all.

00:09:53.240 --> 00:09:54.630
I actually think it's cute.

00:09:54.630 --> 00:09:55.840
But I don't like it.

00:09:57.390 --> 00:09:58.960
I don't like how I am right now.

00:10:00.440 --> 00:10:02.320
That's just how relationships are.

00:10:03.670 --> 00:10:05.120
You become sensitive.

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:06.840
You start overthinking.

00:10:07.790 --> 00:10:09.000
In a relationship,

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.600
that's completely normal.

00:10:11.510 --> 00:10:14.080
Maybe my ex-husband hurt me too deeply.

00:10:16.080 --> 00:10:17.150
It's my own issue.

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:20.320
I don't know what will happen,

00:10:21.790 --> 00:10:24.030
but I don't want to
go back to who I used to be.

00:10:27.150 --> 00:10:28.670
Right now, I want to be single.

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:35.440
Why are you putting your distrust

00:10:35.440 --> 00:10:36.910
of others all on me?

00:10:38.550 --> 00:10:39.790
It wasn't until I met you

00:10:39.790 --> 00:10:41.120
that I realized you're the one.

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:43.510
You're the only right person for me.

00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:45.670
That jerk made you believe

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:49.030
you can't fall in love anymore, but...

00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:54.440
What does that have to do with me loving you?

00:11:01.240 --> 00:11:02.080
Yingtao,

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:04.600
is it wrong for me to love you?

00:11:07.670 --> 00:11:09.080
Please don't leave me.

00:11:09.840 --> 00:11:10.720
Okay?

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:15.680
And then what?

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:18.510
Are you breaking up with him?

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:20.360
Don't be impulsive.

00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:22.150
I haven't decided yet.

00:11:23.690 --> 00:11:24.550
But you see,

00:11:24.560 --> 00:11:26.840
I want to treat every relationship
like it's my first love.

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:28.960
But what happened in the past…

00:11:29.630 --> 00:11:31.320
can't be ignored.

00:11:32.790 --> 00:11:33.910
I didn't see that coming.

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:36.440
Enough about me.

00:11:37.240 --> 00:11:38.480
Are you meeting Lin Chen today?

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:42.360
Just a reminder.

00:11:42.960 --> 00:11:44.840
You've decided to marry Bei.

00:11:44.840 --> 00:11:46.150
Don't take his trust for granted.

00:11:46.960 --> 00:11:48.750
If he finds out one day, even if

00:11:49.030 --> 00:11:50.630
nothing happened between you two,

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:52.030
how do you think he'd take it?

00:11:52.790 --> 00:11:53.630
I know.

00:11:54.440 --> 00:11:56.000
Today's the last time we'll meet.

00:11:56.550 --> 00:11:58.080
After this, I won't hide

00:11:58.080 --> 00:11:59.360
a single thing from Bei.

00:12:02.910 --> 00:12:04.630
It's fine. Even if you do hide something,

00:12:04.910 --> 00:12:06.150
I'll still be on your side.

00:12:06.550 --> 00:12:07.910
What if he hides something from me?

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:09.240
He wouldn't dare.

00:12:14.720 --> 00:12:16.240
I hope Mu can let go of

00:12:16.240 --> 00:12:17.510
pushing Lin Chen away

00:12:17.510 --> 00:12:18.910
and cherish the time they have left.

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:21.510
Why do I feel like you've changed

00:12:21.910 --> 00:12:23.360
towards Lin Chen?

00:12:24.630 --> 00:12:25.670
People change, you know.

00:12:27.150 --> 00:12:28.510
Besides for Bei, does it

00:12:28.510 --> 00:12:30.510
have anything to do with that drama king?

00:12:31.150 --> 00:12:32.510
Who? Gong?

00:12:36.600 --> 00:12:38.360
Yeah. My opinion of him

00:12:38.360 --> 00:12:39.790
has definitely changed.

00:12:40.670 --> 00:12:41.790
He's not going with you today?

00:12:42.080 --> 00:12:42.920
I didn't ask him to.

00:12:44.200 --> 00:12:45.150
But I can tell

00:12:45.150 --> 00:12:46.750
Bei still minds it.

00:12:48.270 --> 00:12:49.320
I think I should

00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:50.840
avoid seeing Gong in private.

00:12:51.150 --> 00:12:51.990
You're right.

00:12:52.670 --> 00:12:54.120
Where are you meeting Lin Chen?

00:12:55.320 --> 00:12:56.440
He's picking me up.

00:13:00.240 --> 00:13:01.270
Where are we?

00:13:02.390 --> 00:13:03.360
It's a guesthouse.

00:13:03.910 --> 00:13:05.240
It's very peaceful.

00:13:06.200 --> 00:13:07.670
I like coming here.

00:13:07.960 --> 00:13:10.030
Being close to nature relaxes me.

00:13:13.670 --> 00:13:14.510
It's beautiful.

00:13:17.080 --> 00:13:17.920
The view is incredible.

00:13:19.910 --> 00:13:20.750
Watch your step.

00:13:22.960 --> 00:13:24.000
Why are we here exactly?

00:13:25.240 --> 00:13:26.150
I was thinking,

00:13:26.150 --> 00:13:27.440
our agreement is almost up.

00:13:28.750 --> 00:13:29.870
Not sure how it'll go for you,

00:13:30.360 --> 00:13:31.200
but...

00:13:31.440 --> 00:13:33.000
I'd like to use my expertise

00:13:33.360 --> 00:13:34.390
to do something for you.

00:13:42.790 --> 00:13:45.030
Have you heard of hypnotherapy?

00:13:45.870 --> 00:13:46.750
Hypnosis?

00:13:49.390 --> 00:13:50.600
I've seen it in movies.

00:13:51.630 --> 00:13:53.750
Does it feel like falling asleep?

00:13:53.960 --> 00:13:55.030
You ask me questions,

00:13:55.030 --> 00:13:56.670
and I just spill everything?

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:00.390
I'm afraid not.

00:14:00.670 --> 00:14:01.600
That's not how it works.

00:14:01.960 --> 00:14:03.600
You'll stay conscious the whole time.

00:14:04.720 --> 00:14:06.150
When we face painful experiences,

00:14:06.150 --> 00:14:07.510
or moments of struggle,

00:14:07.670 --> 00:14:09.630
sometimes we think we've moved on and that

00:14:09.790 --> 00:14:10.670
we don't care anymore.

00:14:10.960 --> 00:14:12.480
Maybe you've even forgotten it,

00:14:12.790 --> 00:14:14.750
but the subconscious never forgets.

00:14:15.360 --> 00:14:17.200
And when you least expect it,

00:14:17.200 --> 00:14:18.910
it resurfaces to haunt you.

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:20.550
Hypnotherapy

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:22.000
can help you

00:14:22.270 --> 00:14:23.870
access your subconscious.

00:14:24.200 --> 00:14:25.790
It helps you see what really

00:14:25.790 --> 00:14:26.840
eating at you.

00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:29.320
But this...

00:14:29.750 --> 00:14:31.600
delves into deeply personal matters.

00:14:31.910 --> 00:14:32.790
So,

00:14:32.790 --> 00:14:33.960
if you're okay with it,

00:14:34.510 --> 00:14:35.600
we can give it a try.

00:14:37.870 --> 00:14:38.710
Okay.

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:46.200
Relax.

00:14:48.240 --> 00:14:49.360
Take a few deep breaths.

00:14:50.630 --> 00:14:53.240
As you breathe, listen to

00:14:53.670 --> 00:14:55.270
the sound of the stream

00:14:55.550 --> 00:14:56.600
and the birds chirping.

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:05.320
Keep your eyes on my pocket watch.

00:15:06.360 --> 00:15:07.200
One.

00:15:08.270 --> 00:15:09.110
Two.

00:15:10.630 --> 00:15:11.470
Three.

00:15:45.030 --> 00:15:46.440
What's happening, Lin Chen?

00:15:49.960 --> 00:15:50.910
Lin Chen?

00:15:52.870 --> 00:15:53.710
Where am I?

00:15:54.630 --> 00:15:55.870
Why can't I move?

00:15:56.270 --> 00:15:57.390
There she is.

00:15:57.910 --> 00:15:59.390
She ruined your happiness.

00:15:59.550 --> 00:16:00.870
Now, she wants to get married?

00:16:00.870 --> 00:16:02.550
What right do you have to be happy?

00:16:02.750 --> 00:16:04.000
You made us suffer so much.

00:16:04.550 --> 00:16:06.600
It was your boyfriends who betrayed you.

00:16:06.870 --> 00:16:07.710
No.

00:16:07.840 --> 00:16:08.720
He loves me.

00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:10.510
He said I'm the only one who matters.

00:16:10.670 --> 00:16:12.240
Everyone else was just a passing thrill.

00:16:12.510 --> 00:16:13.720
Just a fling.

00:16:13.720 --> 00:16:14.960
You've all been deceived.

00:16:16.630 --> 00:16:17.550
Deceived!

00:16:18.750 --> 00:16:19.590
Let me go!

00:16:19.870 --> 00:16:21.720
Even if they aren't good men,

00:16:22.150 --> 00:16:23.550
can you say you're innocent?

00:16:23.550 --> 00:16:24.870
Will you punish

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:26.240
every betrayer?

00:16:26.240 --> 00:16:27.080
Yes.

00:16:27.550 --> 00:16:29.750
You're lying.

00:16:29.910 --> 00:16:32.030
Liar! You are lying. You're lying.

00:16:32.030 --> 00:16:34.270
- You're lying. You are lying.
- Let me go!

00:16:34.270 --> 00:16:36.720
You're lying. You are lying.

00:16:36.870 --> 00:16:38.200
You're lying. You are lying.

00:16:38.360 --> 00:16:42.910
Liar! You are lying. You're lying.

00:16:48.030 --> 00:16:49.720
Good girl, Xiaoxi.

00:16:49.720 --> 00:16:51.750
What wish did you make, Xiaoxi?

00:16:52.390 --> 00:16:53.840
Where is Dad?

00:16:54.550 --> 00:16:55.510
Dad's here.

00:16:59.320 --> 00:17:00.160
Dad.

00:17:02.220 --> 00:17:06.540
